import { Box, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box component="form">
      <TextField
        fullWidth
        id="username"
        label="お名前"
        margin='normal'
        name='username'
        required
      />
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Register
